<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.4.5">
<l>āreṉṉai yārāyvā raṉṉaiyarun tōḻiyaru</l>
<l>nīreṉṉē yeṉṉātē nīḷiravun tuñcuvarāṟ</l>
<l>kāraṉṉa mēṉinaṅ kaṇṇaṉum vārāṉāl</l>
<l>pēreṉṉai māyātāl valviṉaiyēṉ piṉṉiṉṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who will examine me? Mothers and friends,</l>
<l>not saying “what [is it with] you?”, will sleep through all the long night.</l>
<l>My Kaṇṇaṉ too, with cloud-like body, will not come.</l>
<l>[My] name will not hide me with harsh Karma, standing behind [me].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
